#: colordialog.cpp:371
msgctxt "PerceptualColor::ColorDialogPrivate|"
msgid "sRGB"
msgstr "sRGB"

#. @action:button (eye dropper/pipette). A click on the button transforms the mouse cursor to a cross and lets the user choose a color from the screen by doing a left-click. Same text as in QColorDialog
